snippet.title: Minecraft Dungeons Diaries: Creeping Winter DLC
snippet.description:
Join the Minecraft Dungeons team as they walk us through the Creeping Winter DLC that drops on September 8th! Find out more about the merchant and daily trials and discover all the added features such as new mobs, mechanics, artifacts and armors. You may be wondering, why is all this content coming now? Is it because Mojang Studios has run out of ice cream and we need to cool down with some chilled content instead? Watch the video to find out! 

More info: https://www.minecraft.net/en-us/article/new-dungeons-dlc-and-more-september-8
